{"tid":232462,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[錯台重貼] 有線踢爆慈善機構違規向董事發放酬金 其中一間係國際創價學會","createTime":"2017-05-06T18:04:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-06T19:40:57.000Z","uid":43189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b3fd83be09a9ee04f1ec272a71d35b96acc7fe68","tid":232462,"uid":43189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T18:04:50.000Z","msg":"<strong>【跟進審計報告 : 香港國際創價學會 3年間發放1300萬予9董事兼員工】</strong><br />\n<br />\n審計報告揭發多間慈善機構違規向董事發放酬金。立法會政府帳目委員會展開聆訊，稅務局稱沒有權追回款項，又指不向董事發放酬金，並非獲得免稅地位的必要條件<br />\n<br />\n至於審計署提及有一間機構，3年發放共1300萬予9個董事，本台查核資料發現，是指香港國際創價學會。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/671845013007570/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ficablenews%2Fvideos%2F671845013007570%2F&d=WHMLQMiyWmfm849WKe725DA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=05ae0a25\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/671845013007570/</a><br />\n<br />\nfb有留言就話香港創價學會同日本嗰邊係冇關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d5cdbaf4890b52ca0d4344a75624f53ecfb6de4","tid":232462,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T18:08:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"22da1ff66c2ac4c552ad7745d0d074c3cc2562a8","tid":232462,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T18:24:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0cf0bae2d1cdf9337005579871623c8a279f6b3","tid":232462,"uid":43189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T18:26:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪就係呢個組織係西貢撞車死晒啲人</blockquote><br />\n西貢嗰單車禍係香港神慈秀明會"},{"pid":"a9909287fbc2faaa9349ca5d0b3ebcb5e966a742","tid":232462,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T19:40:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}